<\f[B]p\f[R]>
  Click the button to start the animation (disabled by default to protect those
  who suffer migraines when experiencing such animations).
</\f[B]p\f[R]>
<\f[B]p\f[R]>Animations created: <\f[B]span\f[R] id=\(dqcount\-created\(dq>0</\f[B]span\f[R]></\f[B]p\f[R]>
<\f[B]p\f[R]>Animations removed: <\f[B]span\f[R] id=\(dqcount\-removed\(dq>0</\f[B]span\f[R]></\f[B]p\f[R]>
.EE
